# Juice Documentation - Cursor AI Rules

**Last Updated:** January 26, 2026

AI agent guidance for customer-facing Juice documentation (Mintlify).

---

## Project Identity

**Juice Documentation** is a customer-facing documentation site built with Mintlify. It explains how to use Juice for TikTok content creation, account management, and organic growth.

**Audience:** Marketing managers and content creators (non-technical)
**Tone:** Conversational, helpful, friendly
**Format:** Short paragraphs, bullets, visual examples
**Goal:** Help users succeed with Juice, not just list features

**Live URL:** https://docs.juice.co

---

## Technology

- **Mintlify** - Documentation framework
- **MDX** - Markdown with React components
- **42+ pages** across 8 sections

