## Critical Rules

### 1. Tone and Audience

**Write for non-technical users:**
```mdx
// ✅ Good - Conversational, clear
Click the "Generate" button to create your first video. Juice's AI will analyze your brand and create content that matches your style.

// ❌ Bad - Too technical
Execute the content generation API endpoint via the dashboard interface to initialize the AI generation pipeline for your brand kit configuration.
```

**NEVER use technical jargon** - explain in simple terms.

### 2. Mintlify Components

**Use built-in components:**
```mdx
<Steps>
  <Step title="First step">
    Description here
  </Step>
  <Step title="Second step">
    Description here
  </Step>
</Steps>

<Accordion title="Question?">
  Answer here
</Accordion>

<Tip>
  Helpful tip for users
</Tip>

<Warning>
  Important warning
</Warning>

<CardGroup cols={2}>
  <Card title="Feature 1" href="/link">
    Description
  </Card>
  <Card title="Feature 2" href="/link">
    Description
  </Card>
</CardGroup>
```

### 3. Content Structure

**Every page needs:**
```mdx
---
title: "Page Title"
description: "Brief description for SEO"
---

# Page Title

Introduction paragraph explaining what this page covers.

<Note>
Key takeaway or important context
</Note>

## Section 1

Content...

## Section 2

Content...
```

### 4. Navigation Structure

**Defined in [mint.json](mint.json):**
- Update `navigation` array when adding pages
- Keep logical grouping
- Use clear, user-friendly titles

