## Adding New Pages

1. **Create MDX file** in appropriate folder:
```mdx
---
title: "New Feature Guide"
description: "Learn how to use the new feature"
---

# New Feature Guide

Introduction to the feature...

## How It Works

Explanation...

<Steps>
  <Step title="Step 1">
    Instructions...
  </Step>
</Steps>
```

2. **Add to mint.json navigation:**
```json
{
  "group": "Content Creation",
  "pages": [
    "content-creation/existing-page",
    "content-creation/new-feature-guide"
  ]
}
```

3. **Test locally:**
```bash
mintlify dev
```

4. **Deploy:**
```bash
mintlify deploy
```

