## NEVER Rules

1. **NEVER use technical jargon** - write for non-technical users
2. **NEVER skip screenshots** - always include visuals
3. **NEVER write long paragraphs** - keep it scannable
4. **NEVER forget frontmatter** (title, description)
5. **NEVER deploy without testing locally**
6. **NEVER modify mint.json without** testing navigation
7. **NEVER use developer terminology** - use user-friendly language

